## Frontend (Vercel)
# Set this in Vercel so the frontend can call the deployed Render API.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://def-alumni.onrender.com

## Backend (Render)
# Set these in Render for the Express API service.
JWT_SECRET=replace-with-a-long-random-secret
FRONTEND_ORIGIN=https://def-alumni.vercel.app
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://def-alumni.vercel.app,https://your-custom-domain.com
STORAGE_DIR=/var/data

## Local development example
# Use these values only when running the app locally on your machine.
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:4000
# JWT_SECRET=def-dev-secret
# FRONTEND_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173
# CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173
# STORAGE_DIR=./server